I have a 200GB cap, I can't seed all the time. Unfortunately, because I had to change the private bit to upload this to TPB, none of the peers that gave me this file are on this torrent.

According to DHT, there are at least three other seeders. I'll keep drip-seeding the file at 150kb/s, we should have more seeders in a few days.
I'll upload Disc 2 in a few days when my bandwidth cap resets!

First: I'd like to thank you for getting this torrent out here. I've managed to collect the lot of the Plaything series and this is the only one I'm missing.
Second: I was wondering if it would be possible for you to get the naughty disc going so I can complete the collection.
Third: I was wondering how I would go about setting up some torrents of my own here and if there are any in specific you'd like me to try and set up. As I've said, I managed to collect all the Plaything Series, I've only a couple more to complete the Virtual Sex Series and there are a few other Interactives I have. It seems only fair that I try to chip in since this place helped to complete my collections.
